WEBVTT

00:01.078 --> 00:03.679
Previously on <i>Human Target...</i>

00:11.238 --> 00:12.655
Good afternoon.

00:12.722 --> 00:15.164
<i>I think, with your friends'</i>
<i>welfare on the line,</i>

00:15.264 --> 00:17.282
you give me
exactly what I want.

00:24.273 --> 00:26.141
Winston?

00:26.225 --> 00:27.392
You know what to do,
right?

00:27.443 --> 00:28.927
Gonna get him back.

00:35.068 --> 00:37.435
Well, Mr. Winston...

00:39.405 --> 00:41.990
You look very presentable.

00:42.075 --> 00:45.494
I am sorry...
That it had to come to this.

00:45.578 --> 00:47.829
What you had to go through
these last 48 hours

00:47.914 --> 00:49.948
in order to tell me
the truth...

00:52.969 --> 00:54.903
I just can't help
but think

00:54.971 --> 00:56.922
how much better your life
would have turned out

00:56.973 --> 01:00.475
if you'd never met
Christopher Chance.

01:03.629 --> 01:05.230
Enough chitchat.

01:05.297 --> 01:08.316
Let's go get my book.

01:13.806 --> 01:14.823
Next.

01:17.193 --> 01:18.360
<i>How can I help you,</i>
<i>sir?</i>

01:18.444 --> 01:20.529
Morning...Denise.

01:20.613 --> 01:22.497
I'd like to make
a withdrawal.

01:23.833 --> 01:25.650
Certainly.
I can help you with that.

01:25.702 --> 01:27.035
<i>How much?</i>
Uh...Everything.

01:27.120 --> 01:29.121
I'd like to close
my account.

01:29.172 --> 01:31.039
Sorry to hear that.
May I ask why?

01:31.124 --> 01:32.624
Well, I'm gonna be
leaving town

01:32.675 --> 01:35.177
for a little while.

01:37.513 --> 01:41.016
Relax. I'm one of
the good guys.

01:44.137 --> 01:45.670
<i>Chance, they're comin' out.</i>

01:48.524 --> 01:50.726
Denise, would you be a doll

01:50.793 --> 01:52.844
and reach under the counter
and trip the alarm, please?

01:52.895 --> 01:53.845
<i>What's up, bro?</i>

01:53.896 --> 01:54.980
Can't let him get to the door.

01:55.031 --> 01:56.565
<i>This could get messy.</i>

01:59.368 --> 02:01.820
Denise, I'm not
gonna shoot you.

02:01.871 --> 02:05.107
Just reach under the counter
and trip the alarm, please.

02:08.544 --> 02:10.195
What happened?
Where's the sound?

02:10.246 --> 02:12.347
It's a silent alarm.
You're kidding me.

02:12.415 --> 02:14.299
Well, now that you got
what you came for,

02:14.366 --> 02:17.002
answer me one question.

02:17.053 --> 02:18.536
What the hell
is in that book?

02:18.588 --> 02:19.888
Secrets, Mr. Winston,

02:19.972 --> 02:22.507
things the world
does not need to know.

02:22.558 --> 02:26.228
Come on, dude.
It's now or never.

02:29.048 --> 02:31.183
Stay down!

02:31.234 --> 02:33.218
What the hell's going on?

02:33.269 --> 02:35.437
These guys are trying
to rob the place.

02:35.521 --> 02:37.939
<i>Keep them covered.</i>

02:38.024 --> 02:39.891
Mr. Chance!

02:39.942 --> 02:41.392
I was expecting you.

02:41.444 --> 02:43.394
Don't do anything stupid.

02:43.446 --> 02:46.198
Just wanna show you something.

02:54.090 --> 02:55.740
<i>So...</i>

02:55.792 --> 02:57.676
You're gonna put
your guns down.

02:59.095 --> 03:01.129
And we're gonna walk
outta here with my book.

03:01.214 --> 03:04.800
Or you'll be picking up
pieces of him for weeks to come.

03:04.884 --> 03:07.552
Winston...

03:07.603 --> 03:09.471
I'm sorry for getting you
into this mess.

03:09.555 --> 03:11.556
<i>Sorry for whatever torture</i>

03:11.607 --> 03:15.560
you had to endure
because of me.

03:15.611 --> 03:18.830
<i>Most of all...</i>

03:18.898 --> 03:21.817
I'm sorry about
Aunt Suzy.

03:21.901 --> 03:23.401
Aunt Suzy?

03:24.904 --> 03:27.939
Oh, man...
Not aunt Suzy.

03:27.990 --> 03:29.558
You got him?
Yep.

03:32.461 --> 03:34.396
Aah!

03:36.632 --> 03:38.083
<i>Drop your weapons!</i>

03:38.134 --> 03:40.168
<i>Put 'em on the floor!</i>

03:40.253 --> 03:41.920
<i>Down. Put 'em down!</i>

03:43.339 --> 03:45.590
Ehh!

03:45.641 --> 03:46.808
Stop, dude!

03:50.096 --> 03:51.646
Drop 'em!

03:52.815 --> 03:55.466
Smart.

03:55.518 --> 03:57.235
You gotta get this thing
off me, man.

03:57.303 --> 03:58.436
I don't wanna die.

04:00.189 --> 04:01.806
You know how
to diffuse it?

04:01.858 --> 04:05.193
No.

04:05.278 --> 04:06.978
Either way,
this is good-bye.

04:07.029 --> 04:08.697
What?

04:10.032 --> 04:12.083
You ready?

04:12.151 --> 04:13.651
I'm ready.

04:15.000 --> 04:21.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

04:36.008 --> 04:37.976
Chance.

04:38.027 --> 04:39.144
Chance!

04:39.195 --> 04:40.345
We gotta get out of here.

04:40.396 --> 04:42.013
Wait! Where's Chance?

04:42.064 --> 04:43.281
That's it for Chance,
bro.

04:43.349 --> 04:44.515
What are you talking about?

04:44.567 --> 04:45.850
What do you mean?
He's gone.

04:45.902 --> 04:47.518
Dude got too attached.

04:47.570 --> 04:49.354
That's the last you're
ever gonna see of Chance.

04:49.405 --> 04:52.157
Come on.
Come on.

04:58.414 --> 05:01.216
Come on, Winston.
Let's get outta here.

05:12.428 --> 05:15.313
<i>Left you too, huh?</i>

05:22.071 --> 05:24.906
You boys looking for
protection?

05:24.991 --> 05:27.158
We're looking for
Christopher Chance.

05:27.226 --> 05:29.444
Gone.

05:29.528 --> 05:33.031
When will he be back?

05:33.082 --> 05:34.916
Well, that's a good question.

05:37.870 --> 05:40.672
I work for a single employer,
a person of great means,

05:40.739 --> 05:43.174
who is in need
of Mr. Chance's rather...

05:43.242 --> 05:45.460
Specific services.

05:45.544 --> 05:47.212
Any idea
where I might find him?

05:47.279 --> 05:50.749
I don't think
you're gettin' it.

05:50.816 --> 05:52.817
You see,
when I say he's gone,

05:52.885 --> 05:54.752
I don't mean he's down
in Florida taking some R&R

05:54.804 --> 05:57.055
shacked up with a lady
friend somewhere.

05:57.123 --> 05:58.556
I mean gone.
Forever.

05:58.607 --> 06:00.959
Might as well be dead.

06:01.027 --> 06:02.527
You could search
the end of the earth,

06:02.594 --> 06:04.279
and you wouldn't
find him.

06:04.363 --> 06:05.596
Got that?

06:05.648 --> 06:07.232
My employer's
very persistent.

06:07.283 --> 06:09.901
Thank you.

06:09.952 --> 06:13.071
We'll be sure to check
the end of the earth.

06:16.242 --> 06:18.276
Wiseass.

07:42.361 --> 07:44.462
Wow.

07:44.530 --> 07:46.864
I'll give it to you,
Mr. Chance.

07:46.916 --> 07:48.466
When you say
you want to disappear,

07:48.534 --> 07:50.201
you really commit.

07:50.252 --> 07:52.303
<i>It's taken me six months,</i>

07:52.371 --> 07:53.638
an embarrassing
amount of money,

07:53.705 --> 07:55.039
and more time
in a helicopter

07:55.091 --> 07:58.259
than I ever dreamed
my ass would spend.

07:58.344 --> 08:00.762
So I have one thing
to say to you.

08:00.846 --> 08:03.064
You'd better be worth it.

08:13.192 --> 08:17.232
<font color=#7FFF00>♪  Human Target 2x01 ♪</font>
<font color=#FFFF00>Ilsa Pucci</font>
